00:30:00.000 --> 00:30:03.000
And I was at Williamsville, Arkansas, Arkansas like a mile and a half.

00:30:03.000 --> 00:30:09.000
So I walked all the way to Williamsville, Arkansas, Arkansas and told his wife, I got a wall back.

00:30:09.000 --> 00:30:11.000
