00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:44.000
But also on the campus because that was a very important life institution.

00:30:44.000 --> 00:30:53.000
When I got there until Pine Bluff, you know, that was my first big city.

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:58.000
The campus was very pretty. It was really exciting.

00:30:58.000 --> 00:31:13.000
And what helped me jumpstart really fast is that school I went to Oak Grove High School was a very good school.

00:31:13.000 --> 00:31:20.000
And not in fact they had sent about four guys from that school were professors at Pine Bluff.

00:31:20.000 --> 00:31:24.000
And I didn't know that I was before I came along.

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:33.000
And my brother in Milwaukee sent me a letter and said, there is a guy in the vocation school.

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:40.000
You go find him and tell him that child of me, one of the older brother sent you.

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:47.000
He was a Hainan, a Dr. Hainan. And I went there and I walked into his office.

00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:52.000
He looked up and he said, I don't know your name, but you show one of them Jones.

00:31:52.000 --> 00:31:58.000
From Ralston, Willis Meal. And he recognized, oh yeah, you look just like Ernest Jones.

00:31:58.000 --> 00:32:08.000
