00:35:41.000 --> 00:35:51.000
And then he was the one told me, he said, there's some folks in Lurak that's trying to get a civil rights thing started.

00:35:51.000 --> 00:35:54.000
And they want to fill in the Smith.

00:35:54.000 --> 00:36:02.000
