Well, the way I looked at it was if you can be non-violent, the white people would be very

00:44:37.000 --> 00:44:40.000
happy to beat you down.

00:44:40.000 --> 00:44:43.000
They would be very happy doing that to you.

00:44:43.000 --> 00:44:53.000
