00:44:53.000 --> 00:45:05.000
And I felt that if I would be now and the other kids was scared and afraid of it, I think eventually they will come around.

00:45:05.000 --> 00:45:08.000
I told my kids, I'll tell them how they did.

00:45:08.000 --> 00:45:15.000
And I just, and I think what helped me is I wasn't scared.

00:45:15.000 --> 00:45:18.000
I wasn't scared.

00:45:18.000 --> 00:45:32.000
I, my knowledge wasn't good enough to feel that I definitely could win doing it right there.

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:54.000
But I felt that I could see in white people faces that it was working because I saw a young white girl and young white boys come up and would hit me and stuff and run.

00:45:54.000 --> 00:45:57.000
And when I was looking at them, I saw them crying.

00:45:57.000 --> 00:46:00.000
I saw them crying, but they wouldn't focus to see them.

