But I saw them.

00:46:01.000 --> 00:46:08.000
I said, you know, they're doing something they don't want to be doing.

00:46:08.000 --> 00:46:09.000
And I saw that.

00:46:09.000 --> 00:46:18.000
And when I told, like, Grin is that, he said, for real, I said, yeah, you know, they were told to come up and hit us.

